Harmonize tied the knot with his Italian girlfriend Sarah Michelotti last year in a private ceremony. Now Sarah’s best friend Felicia has told Tanzanian blogs the couple are planning to do a second wedding. Harmonize flew to Italy, where he proposed to Sarah in front of her entire family. Months later, they wedded in Tanzania. Felicia says the couple is expected to do another wedding in Italy. Celebrating their first anniversary this year, Harmonize wrote, "Happy anniversary, love of my life." Sarah responded, saying, "Happy anniversarY… 11/05/2016, the day that changed my life. We loved with a love that was more than love." The couple met when Harmonize was still under Diamond Platnumz’s record label and were introduced by manager Sallam Mendez.